      • getCreateInactive

        public java.lang.Boolean getCreateInactive()
        If create_inactive is set to true, then the operation will create the full copy, but not activate the synchronization between source and target volumes. The activation would have to be done using the block volume activate operation. The default value for the parameter is false. That is, the operation will create and activate the synchronization for the full copy.
